      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and sustained care. This automobile has been curated to ensure a seamless transition for its next owner, offering a harmonious balance of performance and aesthetic appeal. Meticulously inspected to ensure it meets our professional standards, it stands as a testament to dependable engineering and responsible ownership. We invite discerning buyers to acquire a vehicle that delivers both enduring value and a sophisticated driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
